{
  "stem": "19837.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Toward the end of the war, we had to take Czech lessons because the Czechoslovakian consulate all of a sudden came into a little money after the war and they let us Czechoslovakian citizens come and eat with them and that was much better food.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But that was just shortly before the war was over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they forced us, we had to take lessons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't have too much to do, just hi and goodbye.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then like they were selling water in the front of the lanes, boiling water, and we had our little sticks to buy boiling water.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we give them the stick and then they offered us alive snakes to eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't buy them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my husband ate from those carts on the street-- he wasn't supposed to-- and he didn't get sick.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I wouldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, we had no problems.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, they spoke-- Chinese people spoke what we called pidgin English.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we we learned to understand that and our English wasn't any better.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it's just like no problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only when we arrived from the mosquito bites.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had-- no, I had a deep hole in my arm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And our doctors, the European doctors, didn't-- first, we had no medications, and second, they didn't know how to treat tropical stuff-- diseases.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they sent me-- I was sent to a Russian doctor who had been living there for years.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he put a little salve on it, and it was gone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I [INAUDIBLE] it for a long time and then everything got, you know, infected.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Henry had prickle-- prickly heat from the terrible heat-- things we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't know how to-- what to do with it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
